OL,3,C10-year-old saddling up to keep Tony
OL,4,CHopper's memory alive
OL,6,FThe family and friends of Carlisle
OL,7,FUnited and Workington Reds hero Tony
OL,8,FHopper are embarking on their latest
OL,9,Ffundraising challenge.
OL,11,FAround 50 people will be taking part
OL,12,Fin the 100-mile cycle from Carlisle to
OL,13,FEdinburgh on Saturday.
OL,15,FThe oldest rider is 70 years old and
OL,16,Fthe youngest is 10-year-old Harry
OL,17,FLittle, who said: "I'm pretty
OL,18,Fconfident about it and I'm looking
OL,19,Fforward to it a lot.
