OL,3,C10-year-old saddling up to keep Tony
OL,4,CHopper's memory alive
OL,6,F"That's where he died in 2018 and he
OL,7,Fhad excellent care," said his wife Sue.
OL,9,FShe added: "Both charities really
OL,10,Fhelped us when Tony was suffering.
OL,12,F"They use the funds to actually care
OL,13,Ffor local people, people in Cumbria,
OL,14,Fwho don't just have MND but have a
OL,15,Fpalliative diagnosis.
OL,17,F"I just love both charities, so it's
OL,18,Fimportant that we keep that going.
