OL,6,F"We're so lucky to have a local
OL,7,Fhospice as well."JSue and Tony's son,
OL,8,FDan Hopper will also be taking part in
OL,9,Fthe challenge on Saturday.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's really important that
OL,12,Fwe do a lot of work to remember my dad
OL,13,Fand raise awareness for him and it's
OL,14,Fsuch a horrible disease and I just
OL,15,Fwant to support anyone that could get
OL,16,FMND."
